                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18261026-79-off434 t18261026-79-cd435"></join>, 4 saws, value 9s. 6d.; 4 planes, value 9s.; 1 saw, value 3s. 6d.; 1 tool-basket, value 10d.; 2 squares, value 5s., and 1 smoothing-plane, value 3s. 6d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
